content.text: The `schools` table has `AdmEmail1` which is the administrator's email. Now let me find the charter school with the fewest students enrolled in K-12 and check its administrator's email.

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT f.CDSCode, f.\`School Name\`, f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\`, s.AdmEmail1 FROM frpm f JOIN schools s ON f.CDSCode = s.CDSCode WHERE f.\`Charter School (Y/N)\` = 1 AND f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\` IS NOT NULL ORDER BY f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\` ASC LIMIT 5;"
